comments: The best lab instructor for CATA 262/263. Willing to take the time to answer every questions and clarify problems. Very nice and clear. His french accent is thick but it just goes with his personality. Love him, i had a great time during labs. Ladies, he\'s got a lot of charm! ;)
JUST AWESOME! Can\'t ask for anyone else then him - Just love him!
This guy is the best! Not only does he explain really well... He is hilarious! Loved going to the labs! The french accent is cute ;).

If you manage to filtrate the useful information from the top french humour, you are gonna get amazing knowledge. He gives you more than any other lab instructor- never mind the europeen PT background and all the rest hundreds of titles. Usually speaks frenglish, but after 2 pm native language takes its part. Has a weakness for winged scapulae:)
